The paper also discusses architectural efforts in designing deeper or wider networks, which suggests it could belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category.

The mention of feature hierarchy and merging structures could suggest a connection to the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-category, which deals with neural networks and their optimization.
